WEBVTT

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Female Ghost: Zhang Peisan! Do you recognize me?

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:27.000
Zhang Peisan: You — who are you?

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:44.000
Female Ghost: I am Xuechun, whom you killed!

00:00:45.000 --> 00:01:02.000
Zhang Peisan: No, impossible! You are already dead!

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:24.000
Female Ghost: You killed me, Zhang Peisan! The crimson palm print is the evidence!

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:50.000
Zhang Peisan: Spare my life, spare my life! I — I confess, I confess!

00:01:51.000 --> 00:02:05.000
Wang Qianjin (removing her disguise): Good! You have confessed in front of everyone!
